\b 35- THE LIGHT METAPHOR THAT COMBINES THE MOMENTS OF CREATION AND DESTRUCTION\b0\par
\par
Yes, light can be a powerful metaphor that unites both the moments of creation and destruction. From a physical, metaphysical and symbolic perspective, light can be seen as an element that brings together the two opposite poles of existence.\par
